<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>{% block title %}johnhull 可視化ポータル{% endblock %}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/style.css">
  <!-- plotly bundled locally -> the whole portal works offline -->
  <script src="assets/plotly.min.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="index.html">johnhull<span>可視化ポータル</span></a>
    <nav>
      <a href="index.html"{% if active == 'index' %} class="on"{% endif %}>ホーム</a>
      <a href="gallery.html"{% if active == 'gallery' %} class="on"{% endif %}>ギャラリー</a>
      <a href="options_core.html"{% if active == 'options_core' %} class="on"{% endif %}>オプション</a>
      <a href="numerics.html"{% if active == 'numerics' %} class="on"{% endif %}>数値</a>
      <a href="risk_credit.html"{% if active == 'risk_credit' %} class="on"{% endif %}>リスク</a>
      <a href="stochastic.html"{% if active == 'stochastic' %} class="on"{% endif %}>確率解析</a>
      <a href="integration.html"{% if active == 'integration' %} class="on"{% endif %}>統合</a>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>
    {% block content %}{% endblock %}
  </main>
  <footer class="foot">
    <p>オフライン自己完結 · plotly ローカル同梱 · 図は <code>hullkit.plotly_viz</code> ビルダーから自動生成(本文と同期)</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
